{"tid":676041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李連杰被指憔悴似老伯 經理人登近照闢謠","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T19:51:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"edca538df5321b72ae4e8cbcaf28ed934e22ed96","tid":676041,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】55歲的李連杰當年在大銀幕打出名堂，成為國際武打明星，怎料近日網上瘋傳其照片，拍得他臉容憔悴、滿頭白髮，加上5年前曾自爆患上甲狀腺機能亢進症（甲亢），需要長期服藥。<br />\n<br />\n有關相片亦引起外國傳媒關注，結果李連杰的經理人Steven Chasman要在《華盛頓郵報》（The Washington Post）中作回應，表示只是相片拍得差，是觀感上的問題，並重申李連杰身體狀態極好，希望不要再有人無中生有。他又發出李連杰近照，直指李連杰對抗甲亢已近10年，不會危及生命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xYQJlM5lBjN7TPXh0U9AIw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180523f214558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxYQJlM5lBjN7TPXh0U9AIw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180523f214558.jpg&h=f4fc033e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%8E%E9%80%A3%E6%9D%B0%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%86%94%E6%82%B4%E4%BC%BC%E8%80%81%E4%BC%AF-%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BB%E8%BF%91%E7%85%A7%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-125100546.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%259D%25B0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2586%2594%25E6%2582%25B4%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BC%25AF-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2585%25A7%25E9%2597%25A2%25E8%25AC%25A0-125100546.html&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=928018c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%8E%E9%80%A3%E6%9D%B0%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%86%94%E6%82%B4%E4%BC%BC%E8%80%81%E4%BC%AF-%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BB%E8%BF%91%E7%85%A7%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-125100546